### Summary of ASX Announcement (Appendix 3G):  
- **Issuance of Performance Rights**: 8,945 unquoted performance rights (AQZAB) issued on 28/05/2025 under an employee incentive scheme (non-KMP executives).  
- **Total Outstanding**: 504,176 unquoted performance rights (AQZAB) on issue post-issuance.  
- **Ordinary Shares**: 160,950,999 quoted ordinary shares (AQZ) on issue.  
- **Approval**: Issued under Listing Rule 7.2 (no shareholder approval required).  

No material trading or capital markets impact identified (routine employee incentive issuance).
